import {Dropdown as BDropdown} from 'react-bootstrap';

export default function Dropdown() {
    return <BDropdown>
        <BDropdown.Toggle id="dropdown-basic">
            Dropdown Button
        </BDropdown.Toggle>
        <BDropdown.Menu>
            <BDropdown.Item href="#/action-1">Action</BDropdown.Item>
            <BDropdown.Item href="#/action-2">Another action</BDropdown.Item>
            <BDropdown.Item href="#/action-3">Something else</BDropdown.Item>
        </BDropdown.Menu>
    </BDropdown>
}
